# 🔦 Flashlight App — App #1

A monetized Flutter flashlight app for Android & iOS.

## Monetization

- **Free users**: Google AdMob banner + interstitial ads
- **Premium users**: $2/month subscription via In-App Purchase (no ads + extra features)

## Premium Features

- SOS Mode (morse code signal)
- Strobe Effect
- Ad-free experience

