## Setup Before Publishing

1. Replace AdMob IDs in `AndroidManifest.xml` and `ios/Runner/Info.plist`
1. Replace AdMob unit IDs in `lib/services/ad_service.dart`
1. Create product ID `flashlight_premium_monthly` in Google Play & App Store Connect
1. Update `applicationId` in `android/app/build.gradle` to your unique package name
1. Update `bundle_identifier` in `codemagic.yaml` to your iOS bundle ID
1. Add keystore + service account credentials to Codemagic

## Codemagic Setup

1. Push this repo to GitHub
1. Connect repo in Codemagic
1. Add Android keystore under Code Signing
1. Add environment variable groups (`google_play_credentials`, `appstore_credentials`)
1. Trigger build!
